</li>
<li id="cite_note-4"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Historical_linguistics#cite_ref-4">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFCampbell1998" class="citation book">Campbell, Lyle (1998). <i>Historical Linguistics: An Introduction</i>. Edinburgh: Edinburgh University Press. p.&#160;391. <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/978_0_7486_4601_2" title="Special:BookSources/978 0 7486 4601 2"><bdi>978 0 7486 4601 2</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Historical+Linguistics%3A+An+Introduction&amp;rft.place=Edinburgh&amp;rft.pages=391&amp;rft.pub=Edinburgh+University+Press&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft.isbn=9780748646012&amp;rft.aulast=Campbell&amp;rft.aufirst=Lyle&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHistorical+linguistics" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
