<li id="cite_note-Routledge_introduction-5"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="Historical_linguistics#cite_ref-Routledge_introduction_5-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="Historical_linguistics#cite_ref-Routledge_introduction_5-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">"Editors' Introduction: Foundations of the new historical linguistics." In. <i>The Routledge Handbook of Historical Linguistics</i> Routledge p.&#160;25.</span>
