<li id="cite_note-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Historical_linguistics#cite_ref-6">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFBaldi2012" class="citation journal"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Philip_Baldi" title="Philip Baldi">Baldi, Philip</a> (2012). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.personal.psu.edu/ped10/Giuli_Dussias/Publications/External/Baldi_Dussias_Rhesis_2012_GD_09_13_2012.pdf">"Historical Linguistics and Cognitive Science"</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>. <i>Rheis, International Journal of Linguistics, Philology and Literature</i>. <b>3</b> (1): 5–27.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Rheis%2C+International+Journal+of+Linguistics%2C+Philology+and+Literature&amp;rft.atitle=Historical+Linguistics+and+Cognitive+Science&amp;rft.volume=3&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=5-27&amp;rft.date=2012&amp;rft.aulast=Baldi&amp;rft.aufirst=Philip&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.personal.psu.edu%2Fped10%2FGiuli_Dussias%2FPublications%2FExternal%2FBaldi_Dussias_Rhesis_2012_GD_09_13_2012.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHistorical+linguistics" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/> p.&#160;11.</span>
